When activating the topology mode, transactions for DB, HTTP(Apache http component) and EJB are tracked by default and the topology information is displayed on the topology dashboard and the X-view.

EJB has been tested in the following environments.

    WebSphere 7, 8.0, 8.5
    WebLogic 10.3.6, 12.1.1, 12.1.2
    JEUS 6.0.X, 7.0.X
    JBoss 6.1.0, 6.2.0, 6.3.0

---

* Default value: true
* Format: Boolean
* Restart: Required
* Related options
    * [enable_socket_wrapper](./agentHelp?key=enable_socket_wrapper&type=1)
    * [topology_http_header_key](./agentHelp?key=topology_http_header_key&type=1)
* Supported version: 5.0.6